data.description: Motivated seller..... Location Location Location!!! Conveniently located in the highly sought after, south Stuart community of Duckwood.  This spacious home is light and bright, and beautifully kept.  Also, huge back room overlooking tropical gardens with fruit trees and mature landscaping, this home is truly Florida living at its Finest!!  Duckwood amenities include heated pool, large clubhouse, active social calendar, nature, bike trail, hobby room and more.
